			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "（2）Linux内核各个版本的代码，知道各个版本的区别"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221110180149-f0urg4f",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221110180149-f0urg4f"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "需要熟练掌握哪些工具？"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\nperf\niperf3\nethtool\nsysbench\nnumactl\n上面的工具基本上要达到所有选项和使用方法都覆盖一遍的程度，因为以下原因的一个或多个：\n（1）性能测试中经常用到\n（2）调试中经常用到\n（3）对我们理解外围设备非常重要"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221110180149-0n2l8cs",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221110180149-0n2l8cs"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "必须看哪些书？"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\n（1）\n《奔跑吧Linux内核》（第2版）卷1，卷2。简称“奔跑书”。\n该书对应Linux 5.0\n（2）\nSystems Performance: Enterprise and the Cloud\n这本书是Brendan D. Gregg写的，非常经典。出了2个版本。\n中文版《性能之巅：洞悉系统、企业与云计算》对应第1版。\n电子书下载：\nSystems Performance: Enterprise and the Cloud\n"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "a",
					"TextMarkAHref": "https://salttiger.com/systems-performance-enterprise-and-the-cloud/",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "https://salttiger.com/systems-performance-enterprise-and-the-cloud/"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\nSystems Performance: Enterprise and the Cloud, 2nd Edition\n"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "a",
					"TextMarkAHref": "https://salttiger.com/systems-performance-enterprise-and-the-cloud-2nd-edition/",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "https://salttiger.com/systems-performance-enterprise-and-the-cloud-2nd-edition/"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221110180149-8kntrn1",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221110180149-8kntrn1"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "哪些书可以做参考？"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\n（1）\n《Linux内核深度解析(基于ARM64架构的Linux4.x内核)》\n该书对应Linux 4.12，也不错。\n（2）\n《用“芯”探核 基于龙芯的Linux内核探索解析》\n该书对应Linux 5.4，对龙芯介绍比较多，内核解析不详尽，但是比较清晰。\n（3）\n其他的经典Linux书籍如LDD，ULK，LKD，《情景分析》，《完全注释》等，对应的内核版本比较老，有时间可以看看。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221110180149-22e8cry",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221110180149-22e8cry"
